Loading Stics daily output file(s)

Source: R/get_daily_results.R
get_daily_results.Rd

Reading daily file(s) as a tibble with possible selection on variables names, cumulative DOY, dates list

get_daily_results(
  workspace,
  usm_name,
  var_list = NULL,
  doy_list = NULL,
  dates_list = NULL
)

Arguments

workspace

Stics or JavaStics workspace path
usm_name

names of the usm
var_list

vector of output variables names (optional)
doy_list

vector of cumulative DOYs (optional)
dates_list

list of dates (optional)

Value

A tibble or a list of

Examples

path <- system.file(file.path("extdata","sti","V9.0"), package = "SticsRFiles")
get_daily_results(path,"banana")
